{"tid":820414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺香港人對呢個風overreact得好緊要","createTime":"2018-09-15T11:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T13:33:40.000Z","uid":150651,"like":35,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b9d9450298ecb604dfcc2b21e14f85c70a44b6d1","tid":820414,"uid":150651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:51:13.000Z","msg":"商戶住戶全部打曬米字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，政府又做疏散，傳媒又不停報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，facebook ig 洗板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，講親話題都係個風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講真，香港呢d傳統沿海大城市，基本上99.99%既基建都已經考慮過防風因素，基本上打風期間，stay係屋企就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n呢幾十年既風，都無咩點造成過人命傷亡，基本上，證明左基建既可信性，同市民既防風意識已經好強<br />\n<br />\n而家個風，成班港豬都唔知咁強調咁驚做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d15dbd8501a4ae073cc70db72ab16007704419c9","tid":820414,"uid":65535,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:55:01.000Z","msg":"吓而家強調個風幾勁要做防風措施痴膠紙咪就係防風意識囉，咁又有得屌，連登仔有乜係唔屌？"},{"pid":"8d071e395ec4dd0fad4b2d5d1f5e0aa5c4542f9b","tid":820414,"uid":51085,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"記得之前打風 有間屋冷氣比人吹入屋<br />\n而家痴下玻璃都要比兒登仔批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd4e43c0f48d44e8a0723e2c73da18da0571916","tid":820414,"uid":8420,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T12:05:38.000Z","msg":"又係你話市民既防風意識已經好強<br />\n市民做防風措施又要屌<br />\n樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdfb457d8ea31b7fb3e49ba56d6c04e01c9856a2","tid":820414,"uid":187585,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T12:05:57.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得大家一起做防風係ok既 不過用膠紙用到缺貨加價真係誇張左 又唔會